query:
SELECT se.*, s.fullName as student_name, s.registrationNumber, sub.name as subject_name, sub.code as subject_code
FROM subjectEnrollments se
JOIN students s ON se.studentId = s.id
JOIN subjects sub ON se.subjectId = sub.id
ORDER BY s.id, sub.name
LIMIT 20;
